Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:24.02,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,300)\fad(1000,0)}地球来客
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:39.84,biaoti2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,285)}另一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}今天的嘉宾是萨塔吉塔·夏马朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 青石先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都两次亲眼目睹到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  不是平时说的那些荒诞的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也没想过你能马上相信我  但我一定会将证据…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}萨塔吉塔·夏马朗先生是在美国的因特网上获得3.0的好评率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}经营着网络宣传销售 被称为新世纪的领军人  在日本出现的众多…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真田啊  说这话可真不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糊掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能让人们开心起来是我的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您理解中的人们的开心究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够活着就是件值得高兴并庆幸的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能够活着的诸位就是真正的成功者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说地球还很原始  但是澡堂还真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后还有期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你说要换身体干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是吃饭洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是觉得帝托不在了更加好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是来到宇宙了  不要这么大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  宇宙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修复你的身体被正式批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这事完全没有听你提起过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在你睡着的时候来的消息  这也不能怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那是你把我打晕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哇哇哇哇哇哇哇  人家听不清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  什么时候才能回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按地球时间来算的话  约一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学校怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就是期中考试了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考试和身体哪个比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,线路频道设定为欧里奥特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宫  快把古文搞定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  明明自己都还没搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天体照片嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宫同学可真浪漫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,悠闲地说着什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下最重要的是下周的考试大山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慌里慌张的男人最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来晚了  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  千川同学还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才来短信说  好像感冒了所以不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起千川的事情  现在最重要的是下周的考试大山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉你负责数学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  大家这个星期天来我家好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去中杉家一起作考前复习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷说想开个聚会来庆祝我康复
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还说要我叫上学校里的朋友一起参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这种场合有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当然会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川那边我会转告的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉的家吗  会是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分普通的房子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉罗  请使用208号入港路线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是巴迪的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟地球一样的蔚蓝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,导航员  莱拉罗使用巴米利恩路线着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 莱拉罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  看到了看到了  那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了啦  安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯  搬运到艾克诺斯奎尔就交给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要花多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这要看精密检查所耗的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能让其尽快恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直都是竭尽全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体真的能够复原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心啦  就连肚脐下面的痣都会给你完美再生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪搜查官  你也需要接受精密检查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请乘坐前来接你的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯的生态矩阵没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一  还是要记录一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神经导电高分子回路的状态也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  出现了少许波动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很大  但果然是只虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是虫子  是麦基乌斯警部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君  请再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应你一定会将你的身体复原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你回到原来生活中去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是虫子  说起话来还真像回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君  抱歉了  暂时就让我和巴迪进行谈话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请  请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托的事情我听说了  我对此非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们会尽可能挽回机能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是需要新的搭档的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警部  打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唯吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗  这次是狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,医学局来了报告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是唯吉·嘉哈乌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两人的精神融合危险指数为绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,精神融合是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是里人格取代表人格的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里人格是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那表人格就是巴迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  我取代了巴迪的话  巴迪会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会从这个世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪内的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  不害怕吗  会消失的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是由于我的失败把你的身体给毁了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没办法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,指数是绿色的话  就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根据艾克诺斯奎尔的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地球时间约三个月就能完成修复了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再过三个月就能把功君的身体复原了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 功君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比预期的早结束真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  有个听说你要回来就十分兴奋的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凯尔兹奥刚才有联络说会来见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  唯吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曾今是我的指导教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪的老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该是在机动公安部…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  别来无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凯尔兹奥教官  很久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很久了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来比试下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没以前有劲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凯尔兹奥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是在与地球人的意识体同居中嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西尽快扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢  你这蜥蜴大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的家伙  出来露个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,教官笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉更冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯凯尔兹奥  不是让你等会的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭上的传唤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  所以你暂时安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上  检查方的询问结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}等等啊  我只是被基加威胁才干的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  接着传讯巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉搜索官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我没有罪  有罪的是基加和巴齐鲁斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被告人肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小题大做  不过是个小喽啰搬运工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要特地叫巴迪来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  似乎是司法局上层的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  请律师进行讯问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:12:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神祇官  奈丘拉·盖泽·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祇官竟然会介入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是越规违法的存在  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪的证人询问不过是审问的借口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在本法庭认可神祇官的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  审问的证言将遵属机密条例
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有个绰号  通称什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反对  证人的绰号与本案无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,证人的实质对本案十分重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反对无效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的绰号是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「狂战士杀手」  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多么勇猛的绰号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个名字正是表现你充满攻击性的个性的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被告人被逮捕的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你却让其他两名重犯逃走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  他们两人携带的违法品是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是警方搜查的机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要忘记这是神祇官的审问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被称之为「硫加」的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是审问  把你知道都说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没人告诉过我关于硫加的详细情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你连两名逃犯携带的东西是什么都不知道的情况下进行搜查的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在对两名逃犯和所携带的不明物硫加进行搜查过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀害了原始星球地球上的一名住民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}原始星球  回虫  是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}搜查官做出这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  共享身体的意识体就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你杀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的提问和本案毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  神祇官的意见过于…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,换我吧  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了  快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在恶意侵犯证人的人权
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反对无效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:15:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不  在下是千川功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被巴迪杀害的…地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本…本法庭暂时休庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祇官认可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 那么… 不是被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然死了但也不全是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  总之我还是这样子活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确和巴迪共用一个身体不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有着种种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过据说身体很快就可以修复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  所以  巴迪没有杀害我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没想到  杀人案的被害者竟然会出来申辩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你作为地球住民的代表  我向你提问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请你回避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不太清楚法庭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道硫加是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在古代帝国语言中就是 「看不见的死」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祇官的脑电波攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把神祇官拥有的历史记录让对方亲身体验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为硫加  比尔盖巴星球的上的所有住民在瞬间死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把此称之为比尔盖巴的惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为硫加？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗  地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是硫加的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果造成比尔盖巴惨剧的硫加在地球的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果地球和比尔盖巴变成同一下场的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗  地球人的坦率的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而巴迪·希冯的冲动搜查的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了让硫加进入地球的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  巴迪已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命做着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祇长监视着你的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要忘记这点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了这里原来是审理你的法庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为神祇官  下达越规法规的判决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要接受精神净化刑25年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是偷渡  不至于这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是神祇官的判决  乖乖接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  在这里提到的关于硫加的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是机密事项  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了传达硫加的情报才来利用这个裁判的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丑话说在前  我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕奥之院是利用奈丘拉故意将硫加的情报传达给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少硫加是帝国的遗产这点已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古代帝国语言中「看不见的死」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  请继续搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是地球人的安全是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还有关于代替之前帝托的拍档一事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要人来代替帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  已经有新的拍档了
